metadata.name: MoonPotatoz #1
metadata.description: If a world didn't have Potatoz, it would be the most tasteless and boring world. Thus, MoonPotatoz, a collection of 7,777 MoonPotatoz, was created and brought to the metaverse for you. Grab a Potatoz and make your best dishes! Inspired by MoonBirds and PotatozLand. Every part is hand-painted, not copied from Moonbirds or PotatozLand, so the owner can have full copyright. This is a CC0 project.
